# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ruff
.ruff_cache/

# Block all markdown files by default
*.md

# Allowlist specific markdown files
!README.md
!LICENSE.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md
